'From Squeak 2.3 of January 14, 1999 on 13 January 1999 at 11:25:45 pm'!"Change Set:		readNextUpdate-swDate:			13 January 1999Author:			Scott WallaceMakes a new expression,   Utilities readNextUpdateFromServeravailable, which will assimilate the next-in-order update.  By repeated evaluation of this expression you can bring in successive updates one at a time in an effort to track down just where something started to behave differently, etc."!!Utilities class methodsFor: 'fetching updates' stamp: 'sw 1/13/1999 23:21'!readNextUpdateFromServer	"Utilities readNextUpdateFromServer"	self updateFromServerThroughUpdateNumber: (ChangeSorter highestNumberedChangeSet + 1)! !